final statement.  Mr. Chen Wei was the subject of a previous communication (see 
A/HRC/18/51, case no. CHN 29/2010). Mr. Chen Xi was the subject of previous 
communications (see A/HRC/13/22/Add. 1, para. 389 and A/HRC/16/44/Add. 1, 
