demonstrators. 70 students were reportedly arrested during the 25 December sit-in. 
On 30 December 2011, Mr. Taj Alsir Jaafar, a student activist, was arrested by 
security forces in Khartoum, presumably for participating in student protests from 
mid-December 2011 into January 2012. On 25 January 2012, six members of the 
student-led movement Girifna were arrested after taking part in a public forum on 
human rights. 
