<p><b>Freedom of 
</b></p>
<p><b>expression;  Human 
</b></p>
<p><b>rights defenders;  
</b></p>
<p><b>Torture;   
</b></p>
<p> 
</p>
<p>Alleged enforced disappearance of 13 human rights defenders in Damascus. 
According to the information received, on 16 February 2012, a security armed patrol 
stormed the offices of the Syrian Centre for Media and Freedom of Expression 
(SCM) and further arrested all 14 persons who were present in the offices. Persons 
arrested include several prominent human rights defenders in Syria. One of them was 
released during the late evening. The fate and whereabouts of the 13 others is 
reportedly unknown 
</p>
<p> 
</p>
<p> 
21/02/2012 
UA 
 
